5.htm|title=Caterpillar Inc \u2013 8-K \u2013 For 2/2/99|publisher=|accessdate=September 21, 2014}}</ref>\n| Rockwell Automation, Inc.\n| Large electrical generators\n|\n|-\n| F.G. Wilson\n| Larne, Northern Ireland\n| 1999<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Jun-1996-8-K\">{{cite web|url=http://edgar.secdatabase.com/1313/1823096000013/filing-main.htm |title=Caterpillar Inc, Form 8-K, Current Report, Filing Date Jun 4, 1996 |publisher=secdatabase.com |accessdate =Mar 20, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2009/jan/08/fg-wilson-job-cuts |title=FG Wilson engineering firm cuts 250 jobs |newspaper=The Guardian |date= January 8, 2009 |author=Henry McDonald |accessdate= November 12, 2014}}</ref>\n| Emerson Electric Company\n| Generators. Produces both Cat and Olympian branded generators\n| Asset swap. Emerson acquired Kato Engineering from Caterpillar as part of transaction.\n|-\n| Earthmoving Equipment Division\n| Chennai, India\n| 2000<ref>[http://www.allbusiness.com/manufacturing/machinery-equipment-manufacturing/8087464-1.html] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205030801/http://www.allbusiness.com/manufacturing/machinery-equipment-manufacturing/8087464-1.html|date=December 5, 2008}}</ref>\n| [[Hindustan Motors]] Ltd.\n| Construction equipment\n| Renamed Caterpillar India and the service & maintenance is provided by birla group's GMMCO Ltd.\n|-\n| Caterpillar Elphinstone\n| [[Burnie]], Australia\n| 2000<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0FZX/is_8_66/ai_64991321 |work=Diesel Progress North American Edition |title=CNH Sells Tractor Operations \u2026 Cat Buys The Rest Of Elphinstone \u2026 Parker Buys Wynn's \u2026 Manitowoc Consolidates \u2013 Brief Article |first=Mike |last=Osenga |year=2000 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160107161102/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m0FZX/is_8_66/ai_64991321 |archivedate=January 7, 2016 }}</ref>\n| [[Elphinstone Group|Elphinstone]]\n| Underground mining equipment\n| Acquired 50% interest in joint venture from partner Elphinstone. Renamed Caterpillar Underground Mining\n|-\n| Sabre Engines Ltd.\n| Wimborne, United Kingdom\n| 2000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/caterpillar-completes-acquisition-of-sabre-engines-ltd-72441587.html|title=Caterpillar Completes Acquisition of Sabre|publisher=|accessdate=August 25, 2016}}</ref>\n| Sabre Group Ltd.\n| Marine diesel engines\n| Renamed Caterpillar Marine Power UK. Produces both Cat and Perkins-Sabre branded engines\n|-\n| Bitelli SpA\n| [[Minerbio]], Italy\n| 2000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rermag.com/mag/equipment_caterpillar_buys_italian/|title=Caterpillar Buys Italian Road Construction Firm|publisher=|accessdate=September 21, 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111108200824/http://rermag.com/mag/equipment_caterpillar_buys_italian/|archive-date=November 8, 2011|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|\n| Asphalt pavers, cold planers, compactors and other road maintenance products\n| Merged into Caterpillar Paving Products\n|-\n| Wealdstone Engineering Ltd.\n| Rushden, United Kingdom\n| 2004<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Feb-2005-DEF-14A\">{{cite web|url=http://pdf.secdatabase.com/997/0001047469-05-004570.pdf |title=Caterpillar Inc, Form DEF 14A, Filing Date Feb 24, 2005 |publisher=secdatabase.com |accessdate =Mar 20, 2013}}</ref>\n|\n| Remanufacturer of gasoline and diesel engines\n| Organized under Caterpillar Remanufacturing Services\n|-\n| Williams Technologies, Inc.\n| Summerville, South Carolina, United States\n| 2004<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Feb-2005-DEF-14A\" />\n| Delco Remy International Inc.\n| Remanufacturer of automatic transmissions, torque converters and engines\n| Organized under Caterpillar Remanufacturing Services\n|-\n| Turbomach SA\n| [[Lavertezzo|Riazzino]], Switzerland\n| 2004<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Feb-2005-10-K\">{{cite web|url=http://edgar.secdatabase.com/175/1823005000218/filing-main.htm |title=Caterpillar Inc, F