4, 2005 |publisher=secdatabase.com |accessdate =Mar 20, 2013}}</ref>\n|\n| Remanufacturer of gasoline and diesel engines\n| Organized under Caterpillar Remanufacturing Services\n|-\n| Williams Technologies, Inc.\n| Summerville, South Carolina, United States\n| 2004<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Feb-2005-DEF-14A\" />\n| Delco Remy International Inc.\n| Remanufacturer of automatic transmissions, torque converters and engines\n| Organized under Caterpillar Remanufacturing Services\n|-\n| Turbomach SA\n| [[Lavertezzo|Riazzino]], Switzerland\n| 2004<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Feb-2005-10-K\">{{cite web|url=http://edgar.secdatabase.com/175/1823005000218/filing-main.htm |title=Caterpillar Inc, Form 10-K, Annual Report, Filing Date Feb 24, 2005 |publisher=secdatabase.com |accessdate =Mar 20, 2013}}</ref>\n| Babcock Borsig AG\n| Packager of industrial gas turbines and related systems\n|\n|-\n| [[Progress Rail]]\n| Albertville, Alabama\n| 2006<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-May-2006-8-K\">{{cite web|url=http://pdf.secdatabase.com/1533/0000018230-06-000243.pdf |title=Caterpillar Inc, Form 8-K, Current Report, Filing Date May 16, 2006 |publisher=secdatabase.com |accessdate =Mar 20, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marketwatch.com/news/story/caterpillar-buys-privately-held-rail/story.aspx?guid={4DAD5133-2E8D-4AB5-957A-0EC7A04FB76D}|title=Caterpillar buys privately held rail services firm for $1B|publisher=|accessdate=September 21, 2014}}</ref>\n| One Equity Partners\n| Supplier of railroad and transit system products and services. Owner of [[Electro-Motive Diesel]]\n|\n|-\n| Hindustan PowerPlus Ltd.\n| Mathagondapalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n| 2006<ref name=\"Caterpillar-Inc-Feb-2007-10-K\">{{cite web|url=http://edgar.secdatabase.com/2676/1823007000053/filing-main.htm |title=Caterpillar Inc, Form 10-K, Annual Report, Filing Date Feb 23, 2007 |publisher=secdatabase.com |accessdate =Mar 20, 2013}}</ref><ref>[http://www.indusbusinessjournal.com/ME2/Audiences/dirmod.asp?sid=&nm=&type